      "description": "Hey there! Are you ready to fall in love? I\u2019m parting ways with my absolute gem of a car, and honestly, it\u2019s in such incredible shape it still feels brand new! It\u2019s been pampered since day one, kept tucked away in a garage, and looks absolutely stunning inside and out. No scratches, no spills, just pure driving bliss. It\u2019s rare to find one this pristine, so come grab it before someone else does! I'd love to see it go to a great home\u2014let\u2019s get you behind the wheel of your dream ride today!",
