    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This AP2 chassis represents the pinnacle of naturally aspirated engineering, featuring the high-revving F22C1 power plant mated to a precise, close-ratio six-speed manual transmission. This example is in showroom condition, retaining all original factory VIN tags and an immaculate undercarriage. The Torsen limited-slip differential and double-wishbone suspension remain strictly factory-spec, delivering the razor-sharp turn-in and perfect 50/50 weight distribution that defined the S2000's legacy. With zero oxidation on the longitudinal aluminum block and a flawless power-folding soft top, this is a collector-grade specimen for the discerning purist.",
      "price": 48500.0,
